data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. *Back on the market* Passed Inspections- Appraisal - No fault to the seller- Priced to sell quick-  Artsy retro home nestled in a quiet neighborhood where vintage charm meets modern comfort...a truly one of a kind...welcome home! “Living Room was converted as a 3rd bedroom.” From the moment you walk into the door you will fall in love with the stunning wood floors, and the oh so tasteful soft palate on the walls helping to awaken the artist in you.  You will delight in displaying your colorful artwork and special family photos! This home radiates a warmth that only a home that has been truly loved exhibits.   The master bedroom is a sanctuary, with its own private bathroom and walk-in closet. The second bedroom is a versatile space that can be used as an office, family room, or guest room. The third bedroom is a cozy retreat, with a well appointed closet and easy access to the second bathroom. The living room is very spacious and a perfect place to relax and unwind.  This home even comes complete with a huge flat screen TV with a home theatre sound device included!  Who could ask for more!  The kitchen is reminiscent of a chic farmhouse style with all the amenities that you need.  There is even a touch of elegance with the placement of the lights under the cabinet as you meet with your loved ones for a late night snack.  And that’s not all, the large farmhouse sink makes cleaning up the dishes a joy, and adds a great artsy retro look!  Who would of thought doing dishes could be fun? But the true gem of this home is the sunlit indoor Florida room. This sun-drenched space is the perfect place to enjoy a cup of coffee in the morning, read a book in the afternoon, entertain guests in the evening. or, maybe you prefer to convert it to an artist’s studio! You will know what it is to enjoy life as you gaze into your nicely landscaped backyard with shade trees and bright flowers while listening to the chirping sounds of your favorite birds..  There is also a solid wood fence for your furry friends. But wait...there is more... a very convenient storage shed has been added, complete with its own A/C unit.  This is a great added space for the dreamer in you. The two car garage includes a refrigerator, and a washer and dryer.  This home is the perfect place to create a life filled with beauty, creativity, and connection.  Whether you are an artist, a writer, a professional working remotely or just a lover of the unique, this farmhouse is the place you will want to call home. Please set up an appointment to see this home today!
